name: Laci Kay Somers (Instagram model)
description:
A request of @bobbyb242

Laci Kay Somers is an Instagram model, singer and actress. I have trained her TI on 30 images, during 4000 steps and with a gradual learning rate (0.05:10, 0.02:20, 0.01:60, 0.005:200, 0.002:500, 0.001:3000, 0.0005). This one is performing much better than my previous embedding, and should do well in most models, I reckon. Hope you like it!

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: A less saturated version of the same embedding, taken from step 1700 (out of 4000). Looks at least as accurate as the final one (possibly more so).
